Explore Emscripten, an LLVM-based compiler that translates C++ code into JavaScript for near-native web speeds. This talk details how it achieves this performance, including the use of asm.js, a JavaScript subset. Learn about the challenges of compiling C++ to JavaScript and potential solutions.
